name: easily animated hip sway dance（Zero two DANCE） 简易的臀部摇摆舞动画
description:
这个模型生成的结果有些糟糕，可能需要您手动地对分割后的图像进行排序以达到较好的效果。

这个Lora模型是基于final-prune.ckpt（【旧短哈希1d4a34af】新短哈希22fa233c2d）训练出的。

1.使用768x768的分辨率生成图像

2.使用photosop等软件分割图像

3.分别保存这些图像并使用诸如ezgif的网站或者工具来创建你的 gif 动画

您也可以使用1024x1024的分辨率生成图像，但这可能会生成不稳定的结果。

灵感来源自easily animated deepthroat concept style [TEST].

推荐权重为0.8。

英语是用Google翻译翻译的，如果有造成误解之处非常抱歉。

This model produces somewhat poor results and may require you to manually sort the segmented images to achieve good results.

This Lora model is trained based on final-prune.ckpt ([old short hash 1d4a34af] new short hash 22fa233c2d).

1. Generate images with a resolution of 768x768

2. Use software such as photosop to segment the image

3. Save these images separately and use a website or tool like ezgif to create your animated gif

You can also generate images with a resolution of 1024x1024, but this may produce unstable results.

Inspired by easily animated deepthroat concept style [TEST].

The recommended weight is 0.8.

English is translated by Google Translate, sorry if there is any misunderstanding.
